// 4 - MXMTypeA: Mobile PCI Express Module (MXM) Type A form factor (compact laptop/embedded GPU module).
// 5 - MXMTypeB: Mobile PCI Express Module (MXM) Type B form factor (larger laptop/embedded GPU module).
// 6 - 2: M.2 (NGFF) internal module form factor/connector exposing PCIe (and/or SATA/USB) for SSDs and add‑in modules.
// 7 - CXL: Compute Express Link (CXL), an open cache‑coherent interconnect for processors, memory expansion, and accelerators built on the PCIe physical layer.
